<p><span class=atitle><b>SYMPOSIUM IS GREEK FOR PARTY!</b><br></span>
<span class=asubtitle>Cast a glance at the 2nd Greek BookCrossing Convention in Athens<br></span>
by <a href="http://www.bookcrossing.com/mybookshelf/aris1"><b>* (aris1)</b></a></p>
<p>
<img src="http://farm1.static.flickr.com/193/474419508_d8409aa563_m.jpg" align=left hspace=5 height=190px>The Athens Symposium was quite a blast! About 70 BookCrossers 
from all over Greece and even the UK joined the party and had a great time. We really enjoyed strolling in sunny Athens, making new friends, meeting old 
ones, drinking wine, eating souvlaki, philosophizing, and releasing loads of books! ...
