<p><span class=atitle><b>RELEASE YOUR BOOKS IN SUNNY NICE!</b><br></span>
<span class=asubtitle>MBC on Saturday, 23 June in Nice, France - Big release event<br></span>
by <a href="http://www.bookcrossing.com/mybookshelf/KanaPoutz"><b>KanaPoutz</b></a></p>
