<img src="http://mbc2007.bookcrossers.it/images/mbc2007.jpg" align=left hspace=5>French BookCrossers are happy to announce that the 11th MBC will take place 
in Nice, on Saturday, 23 June!  BookCrossers will meet and release their books in the great setting of the castle hill, overlooking the Mediterranean and 
the old town....
